Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.89,0:01:41.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是在世界各地展開了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.29,0:02:22.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那成為了新一輪戰鬥的開端
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(title)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.34,0:03:14.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開球了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.01,0:03:28.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnSource Han Serif TC Heavy\bord0\pos(520,332)\fs65}今日午餐\N{\c&H8BD5E2&}一騎咖喱\N{\c&HAF85C5&}（有一騎蛋糕）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.32,0:03:28.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.83,0:03:30.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您的一騎咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.33,0:03:32.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}好像很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.01,0:03:32.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您要點些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.36,0:03:34.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.33,0:03:36.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 B桌兩份
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.34,0:03:37.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溝口先生 這是追加的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.42,0:03:48.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎咖喱 追加兩份
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.59,0:03:50.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饒了我吧 溝口先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.11,0:03:52.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別把料理套上我的名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.15,0:03:55.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰讓你是這兒的招牌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.41,0:03:57.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溝口先生 外賣 Alvis叫的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.88,0:03:58.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.09,0:04:02.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天可還有祭典啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.45,0:04:12.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在開始對本年度U計劃做最後一次確認
